<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>إِسْلاَمٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> سَلَم<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِسْلاَفٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> سَلَف<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِسْنَادٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> الإِْسْنَادُ لُغَةً يَكُونُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أ - بِمَعْنَى إِمَالَةِ الشَّيْءِ إِلَى الشَّيْءِ حَتَّى يَعْتَمِدَ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ب - وَيَأْتِي أَيْضًا بِمَعْنَى رَفْعِ الْقَوْل إِلَى قَائِلِهِ وَنِسْبَتِهِ إِلَيْهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<span class="c5"> وَيَأْتِي اصْطِلاَحًا لِمَعَانٍ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أ - إِعَانَةُ الْغَيْرِ، كَالْمَرِيضِ مَثَلاً، بِتَمْكِينِهِ مِنَ التَّوَكُّؤِ عَلَى الْمُسْنَدِ، وَنَحْوُهُ إِسْنَادُ الظَّهْرِ إِلَى الشَّيْءِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَتَفْصِيل الْكَلاَمِ فِي الإِْسْنَادِ بِهَذَا الْمَعْنَى يَأْتِي تَحْتَ عِنْوَانَيِ:</span> <span class="c2">(اسْتِنَاد)</span> <span class="c2">(وَإِعَانَة)</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) لسان العرب، ومعجم متن اللغة، وتاج العروس مادة: (سند) .</p> </div>